portedException();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public <T> T unwrap(Class<T> iface) throws SQLException {\n            throw new SQLException(\"No wrapped data source is available.\");\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public boolean isWrapperFor(Class<?> iface) {\n            return false;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777526132021}]}
